org.apache.avro

Class SchemaBuilder.UnionFieldTypeBuilder<R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.avro.SchemaBuilder.UnionFieldTypeBuilder<R>
  • Enclosing class:
    SchemaBuilder

    public static final class SchemaBuilder.UnionFieldTypeBuilder<R>
extends Object
    Builder for a union field. The first type in the union corresponds to the possible default value type.
